title: Wlaad Al Baher Win Red Bull Reign in Kuwait

organizations.name: wlaad al baher win red bull reign in kuwait wlaad al baher win red bull reign

text:
Wlaad Al Baher Win Red Bull Reign in Kuwait By Red Bull Kuwait on 18 February 2017 
Team Wlaad Al Baher won the maiden Red Bull Reign 3 VS 3 Basketball event after overcoming a tough competition in the final besting team Los Andalus 5-4. 
Red Bull Reign took place over 3 days at the Marina World Basketball courts and hosted 48 teams & 192 players. 
With this win, Wlaad Al Baher will represent Kuwait in the world final, which will bring together all finalists from other countries, in Washington in the US this coming September. read more about
